" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ce94906 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"ce94906\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-95ea88b elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"95ea88b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17cc5e9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"17cc5e9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">An Improved Block Editor With New Useful Features\n</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-85fee3f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"85fee3f\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab43d8c elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"ab43d8c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca06f1c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ca06f1c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As you might already know, back in 2018, WordPress made the block editor </span><b>Gutenberg </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">its default editor to enhance our writing experience. With the release of WordPress 5.5, the Gutenberg editor is now much better and comes with many significant features to improve user experience. Below, weve listed some of the new things you will get with this improved version of WordPress block editor.</span></p><h3><b>Enhanced User Interface For Better Experience With The Block Editor</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The user interface for the Gutenberg editor will be revamped with the release of WordPress 5.5 for a better user experience. For instance, the </span><b>+</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> icon for adding new blocks has been changed to make it more visible and look more like a button. You can also notice borders and focus highlights when moving from one block to another.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To get a better understanding, you can move the slider below to get a better comparison of the previous block editor <strong>(shown on the first slide)</strong> and the new improved version that comes with WordPress 5.5 <strong>(shown on the second slide)</strong>.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-44cdbd2 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"44cdbd2\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b2b7cfb elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"b2b7cfb\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83d588e elementor-arrows-position-inside elementor-pagination-position-outside elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-carousel\" data-id=\"83d588e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;slides_to_show&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;navigation&quot;:&quot;both&quot;,&quot;autoplay&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;pause_on_hover&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;pause_on_interaction&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;autoplay_speed&quot;:5000,&quot;infinite&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;effect&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;,&quot;speed&quot;:500,&quot;direction&quot;:&quot;ltr&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image-carousel.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image-carousel-wrapper swiper-container\" dir=\"ltr\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-image-carousel swiper-wrapper swiper-image-stretch\">\n				<div class=\"swiper-slide\"><figure class=\"swiper-slide-inner\"><img class=\"swiper-slide-image\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1-2.png\" alt=\"WordPress 5.5 Next Release\" /><figcaption class=\"elementor-image-carousel-caption\">WordPress 5.4.2 Block Editor</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\"><figure class=\"swiper-slide-inner\"><img class=\"swiper-slide-image\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1-1-1.png\" alt=\"WordPress 5.5 Block Editor\" /><figcaption class=\"elementor-image-carousel-caption\">WordPress 5.5 Block Editor</figcaption></figure></div>			</div>\n												<div class=\"swiper-pagination\"></div>\n													<div class=\"elementor-swiper-button elementor-swiper-button-prev\">\n						<i class=\"eicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n						<span class=\"elementor-screen-only\">Previous</span>\n					</div>\n					<div class=\"elementor-swiper-button elementor-swiper-button-next\">\n						<i class=\"eicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n						<span class=\"elementor-screen-only\">Next</span>\n					</div>\n									</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c5dcdc elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"3c5dcdc\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-da51aa6 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"da51aa6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-da9a4a7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"da9a4a7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>A New Block Directory To Quickly Find New Blocks</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Perhaps one of the best features of WordPresss new and improved block editor is that you can quickly search for the blocks you might need for your content with the new block directory feature.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Simply search for any block that you might need, and the block directory will pull up the best matching results for you based on WordPresss list of</span><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/browse/block/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b> plugins categorized as blocks</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3000d46 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"3000d46\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58080d6 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"58080d6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e23cbb1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e23cbb1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1920\" height=\"935\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"WordPress 5.5 Next Release\" srcset=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2.png 1920w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-600x292.png 600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-1600x779.png 1600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-768x374.png 768w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-1536x748.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e80bfcf 